{"tid":495528,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返工能有朋友嗎？","createTime":"2017-12-10T18:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T03:49:59.000Z","uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf3e5100654115a18a0dc536293168099f57a18","tid":495528,"uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T18:29:04.000Z","msg":"有時見人返工可以同同事稱兄道弟，或者知己，放工後仲會約埋一齊玩，有時都幾羨慕佢地。 <br />\n自己同同事關係唔係差，但唔會去到傾心事，平時只係工作時吹兩句水，放工就拜拜。一直好想同同事有果種齊齊拍住上果種感覺。<br />\n唯有同自己講，返工為份糧，有朋友當bonus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ffb83b5a47e18517c3de4a3c18fd64d4fa33d7","tid":495528,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"翻工不要想太多"},{"pid":"010b8e7ca72da1f28c21dcc8544a31b376abfba5","tid":495528,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"最了解你既人<br />\n往往會出賣你"},{"pid":"8ec6405ca5e37385617a4eaed13dce2051547a44","tid":495528,"uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T18:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最了解你既人<br />\n往往會出賣你</blockquote><br />\n有時唔知係咪愈做得耐，愈有經驗就愈明白呢個道理，我見身邊既senior,工作堆又無朋友，究竟點解可以捱到而家"},{"pid":"6439734dd10b945ec7822e7e20a35849b6deef90","tid":495528,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:42:55.000Z","msg":"分兩類<br />\n一類 有得升職 有得爭業績 就一定無<br />\n另一類 hea下hea下又一日個種 就有<br />\n同埋 君子之交淡如水  大個仔就唔好成日覺得朋友好重要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f5006c690334532046e0ea524dbfefe8500ebf","tid":495528,"uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}